563
00:56:21.250 --> 00:56:22.916
Who are you?

564
00:56:23.083 --> 00:56:24.250
Why?

565
00:56:25.958 --> 00:56:28.833
A new beginning.

566
00:56:36.375 --> 00:56:37.833
No. Don't take...

567
