622
01:00:24.125 --> 01:00:25.375
What is that?

623
01:00:27.458 --> 01:00:27.916
Shit.

624
01:00:28.083 --> 01:00:29.208
Let's go!

625
01:00:31.541 --> 01:00:32.708
Through here.

626
