640
01:01:28.791 --> 01:01:29.875
Stay down, stay down.

641
01:01:30.041 --> 01:01:31.458
Where'd he go?

642
01:01:33.208 --> 01:01:34.208
Where'd he go?

643
01:01:34.583 --> 01:01:35.583
