what I lost.

693
01:07:49.833 --> 01:07:51.666
He'll give you even more.

694
01:07:55.750 --> 01:07:57.333
Look.

695
01:08:00.083 --> 01:08:01.291
Mommy.

696
01:08:07.750 --> 01:08:08.833
Did he speak to you?

697
01:08:12.791 --> 01:08:14.166
What?

698
01:08:15.041 --> 01:08:15.833
In your dream.

699
01:08:16.000 --> 01:08:17.250
