700
01:08:20.000 --> 01:08:21.000
Laura.

701
01:08:22.208 --> 01:08:24.958
I want to tell you a story.

702
01:08:27.416 --> 01:08:31.291
About a brave warrior
who stood up to

703
01:08:31.458 --> 01:08:33.250
