767
01:13:46.500 --> 01:13:47.791
My child?

768
01:13:47.958 --> 01:13:49.041
No.

769
01:13:49.208 --> 01:13:51.708
I've given you a child to love.

770
01:13:51.875 --> 01:13:54.666
I hate what that murderer
did to you.

771
01:13:54.833 --> 01:13:57.250
